race.comment: SACHEM (3) is third-up and looks ready to win. There has been merit in both of his run over a shorter trip and he's won over 1600m previously. From barrier four, he might not have to concede a big start. LOMAX (4) is a three-time winner at the track and distance. Drops back from 1800m to the mile which he placed at two starts ago. SWYCHO (7) has been only fair this preparation but her best form would stack right up. Ran fifth off a freshen up here three weeks ago. Will be fitter for that and is a winner at this course and distance. SUPER LAD (5) is racing with confidence. Comes here looking for a hat-trick after consecutive wins at Balaklava. SAVASONIC (6) next elect off a strong first up win at this course. Clearly back on track after some poor runs late last season. Something for the Multiples: LIFT THE BAR (11)
